ActCanada Shipping Act, 2001
SubjectRegulations Amending the Vessel Operation Restriction Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE VESSEL OPERATION RESTRICTION REGULATIONS which contain a year-round prohibition on recreational towing activities in order to protect wetlands of international importance and restrictions on the speed of vessels to enhance safety and reduce the risk of injury, death, or property damage for waterway users.
